               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Name of the donor; incipit of Text I-1; initial line or word śäräqä introducing the month; Ethiopic numeral of the day; words indicating the time of reading: bä-mäḥatǝw, zä-nägh, qǝdmä wangel; titles of books to be read; incipit of Text I-2 and its sections; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals; the directives to the ministers ʾǝskä ḫabä yǝbǝl “let him say till”; names of months Mäskäräm, Ṭǝqǝmt, Näḥase and Ṗagwǝmen written in the upper margin (the others are in black).&#xD;
On the incipit page of Texts I-1 and I-2, a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines).</rubric>
